reviewText: My Grandchildren like to watch my copy.  Now they will have their own copy for Christmas.
these bunnies are great entertainment for my 3yr old granddaughter.
Family friendly, my daughter enjoys watching it over and over again! Great follow up to the first movie in the series we have.

We came across the Bellflower bunnies accidentally when my older daughter (now 6) was barely two. She as well as my 3-year-old continue to enjoy all the adventures of the bunnies, which are sweet and engaging even for adults. We have by now 6 different DVDs of the Bellflower Bunnies and they are all worth it.
